@startuml
title UC2 — Assign and Track Work Order (High-Level)

actor Supervisor
participant "Maintenance Management System" as MMS
participant "Notification Service" as Notif
actor Technician

Supervisor -> MMS : Assign work order
MMS -> Notif : Send work order notification
Notif -> Technician : Notify assigned work order
MMS --> Supervisor : Confirm assignment

Supervisor -> MMS : Track work order status
MMS --> Supervisor : Return work order status

@enduml